Charlie Sumner staged a one-man pitch invasion during Reading's FA Cup quarter-final win over Bradford City last month . 
  The 20-year-old ran on to the pitch topless and did four front flips on the pitch . 
  He faces a potential three-year ban and said he has no regrets about the stunt . 
  The Royals fan said it was his first game at the Madejski Stadium . 
  He was tackled by stewards and footage of his antics went viral . 
 